Dialogue: 9,0:00:07.21,0:00:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 9,0:00:09.06,0:00:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 9,0:00:10.17,0:00:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you come here?
Dialogue: 9,0:00:11.90,0:00:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Now everything I did was in vain!
Dialogue: 9,0:00:15.04,0:00:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you think I—
Dialogue: 9,0:00:16.20,0:00:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 9,0:00:17.87,0:00:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,"Live on"?
Dialogue: 9,0:00:20.92,0:00:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"Become a normal person"?
Dialogue: 9,0:00:23.96,0:00:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell wished for that?
Dialogue: 9,0:00:25.67,0:00:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell asked for that crap?!
Dialogue: 9,0:00:28.67,0:00:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,How unpleasant!
Dialogue: 9,0:00:30.06,0:00:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,How utterly unpleasant!
Dialogue: 9,0:00:32.50,0:00:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm{\i0} the one who should be feeling unpleasant!
Dialogue: 9,0:00:34.52,0:00:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I refuse to stand for this!
Dialogue: 9,0:00:36.73,0:00:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want a life that was\Nbuilt on your sacrifice.
Dialogue: 9,0:00:39.72,0:00:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,A future like that...
Dialogue: 9,0:00:41.28,0:00:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,holds no meaning at all!
Dialogue: 9,0:00:43.52,0:00:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you understand that?!
Dialogue: 9,0:00:47.90,0:00:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Why was that so difficult for you to understand?
Dialogue: 9,0:00:58.74,0:01:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought I'd run into you here,
Dialogue: 9,0:01:01.53,0:01:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanbara Yayoi.
Dialogue: 9,0:01:02.55,0:01:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Long time no see.
Dialogue: 9,0:01:04.16,0:01:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hop you've grown, Izumin.
Dialogue: 9,0:01:06.58,0:01:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to kick her.
Dialogue: 9,0:01:07.85,0:01:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you after?
Dialogue: 9,0:01:09.39,0:01:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly is your relationship with Kanbara Akihito?
Dialogue: 9,0:01:11.65,0:01:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,"What"? Akkun's my little fella!
Dialogue: 9,0:01:14.49,0:01:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and I didn't mean anything bunny by that—
Dialogue: 9,0:01:19.48,0:01:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't take it any more.
Dialogue: 9,0:01:21.25,0:01:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 9,0:01:22.37,0:01:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hadn't done it, I would have.
Dialogue: 9,0:01:24.75,0:01:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer my questions.
Dialogue: 9,0:01:26.72,0:01:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your relationship\Nwith the immortal half-shade?
Dialogue: 9,0:01:28.77,0:01:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you after?
Dialogue: 9,0:01:30.53,0:01:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I carrot believe you'd ask such stupid questions. You're no fun anymore, Izumin.
Dialogue: 9,0:01:35.40,0:01:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't have grown up\N\hto be that kind of adult—
Dialogue: 9,0:01:39.58,0:01:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I chose to be like this.
Dialogue: 9,0:01:42.28,0:01:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi...
Dialogue: 9,0:01:44.40,0:01:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi-neesan!
Dialogue: 9,0:01:48.04,0:01:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,A double!
Dialogue: 9,0:01:50.30,0:01:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,When will you stop dragging these kids into us adults' nonsense?
Dialogue: 9,0:01:54.28,0:01:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The Spirit Hunters' Association has already made its move, you know?
Dialogue: 9,0:02:02.10,0:02:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiro'omi-kun, Mitsuki-chan.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:04.40,0:02:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Akihito and Mirai-chan are more than\N\hjust a dreamshade and a spirit hunter—
Dialogue: 9,0:02:07.97,0:02:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,they're special.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:12.11,0:02:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I leave them in your care!
Dialogue: 9,0:02:13.96,0:02:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,To be continued!
Dialogue: 9,0:02:14.86,0:02:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 9,0:02:15.34,0:02:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Nee-san!
Dialogue: 9,0:02:16.63,0:02:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now,
Dialogue: 9,0:02:19.64,0:02:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,shouldn't that beam of light take priority?
Dialogue: 9,0:02:22.05,0:02:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez!
