Dialogue: 9,0:02:22.87,0:02:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,How can anyone call that\Nabsurd thing a dreamshade?
Dialogue: 9,0:02:25.69,0:02:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ask me!
Dialogue: 9,0:02:26.97,0:02:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You were the one who was harboring it to begin with!
Dialogue: 9,0:02:29.73,0:02:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just the core.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:31.96,0:02:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,In truth, everything around us was inside you.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:37.17,0:02:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder my back's been killing me.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:39.49,0:02:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no time to be joking around!
Dialogue: 9,0:02:48.50,0:02:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai,
Dialogue: 9,0:02:49.47,0:02:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,have you come up with anything yet?
Dialogue: 9,0:02:50.93,0:02:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 9,0:02:52.15,0:02:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a weakness or something!
Dialogue: 9,0:02:53.91,0:02:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, maybe it has\Nsensitive armpits like you.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:57.74,0:02:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Armpits?
Dialogue: 9,0:02:59.45,0:03:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Where exactly?!
Dialogue: 9,0:03:01.14,0:03:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... do you have something you hate?
Dialogue: 9,0:03:04.07,0:03:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything will do.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:05.45,0:03:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Something I hate, huh?
Dialogue: 9,0:03:09.32,0:03:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Capelin with roe?
Dialogue: 9,0:03:11.54,0:03:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Capelin with roe!
Dialogue: 9,0:03:16.30,0:03:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Think it's mad now?
Dialogue: 9,0:03:17.27,0:03:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ask me!
Dialogue: 9,0:03:30.81,0:03:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuriyama-san!
Dialogue: 9,0:03:46.33,0:03:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you just do that?
Dialogue: 9,0:03:48.15,0:03:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:50.16,0:03:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you have a shade hand now?
Dialogue: 9,0:03:55.98,0:04:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That shadestone was a part of the\Nshade beyond the horizon—a part of you?
Dialogue: 9,0:04:01.64,0:04:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:02.73,0:04:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai, you hold a part of its \Npowers in your hand right now!
Dialogue: 9,0:04:07.78,0:04:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure how we'll manage,
Dialogue: 9,0:04:09.61,0:04:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,but if you can stand up to it...
Dialogue: 9,0:04:13.94,0:04:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...then it might be worth getting closer.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:17.50,0:04:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it hasn't finished eating just yet.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:19.90,0:04:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that how strong the shade from beyond the horizon is?
Dialogue: 9,0:04:23.49,0:04:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Or does that reflect how \Nstrong-willed Kuriyama Mirai is?
Dialogue: 9,0:04:26.80,0:04:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The latter, obviously.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:30.66,0:04:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, you're pretty handsome.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:33.75,0:04:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Not my type, though.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:36.73,0:04:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems some of my powers have returned thanks to the efforts of those two.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:41.87,0:04:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, should be enough to defeat you—
Dialogue: 9,0:04:43.51,0:04:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not interested in you.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:48.32,0:04:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure took your time today, eh?
Dialogue: 9,0:04:50.14,0:04:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You kept me waiting.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:02.50,0:05:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's grown rather powerful, don't you think?
Dialogue: 9,0:05:04.73,0:05:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,By feeding off the Hollow Shade you had at your place,
Dialogue: 9,0:05:07.36,0:05:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,it's finally starting to take its rightful shape.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:24.38,0:05:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately for you,
Dialogue: 9,0:05:25.99,0:05:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I stalk anyone who so much as lays a finger on\Nmy little sister, waiting for the chance to crush them.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:31.84,0:05:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Three-on-one, huh?
Dialogue: 9,0:05:33.55,0:05:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:34.56,0:05:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Four-on-one.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:36.02,0:05:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuki?
Dialogue: 9,0:05:37.14,0:05:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because I was the last-born,
Dialogue: 9,0:05:39.07,0:05:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had to sit tight at home all my life.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:41.65,0:05:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about time I moved on from that.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:44.40,0:05:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Likewise.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:46.42,0:05:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I was the one who originally wielded that scythe.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:49.57,0:05:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to take responsibility for my actions.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:51.53,0:05:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness me,
Dialogue: 9,0:05:53.17,0:05:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,you people are getting along pretty well all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:58.08,0:05:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Nee-sama!
Dialogue: 9,0:05:58.71,0:05:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 9,0:06:03.32,0:06:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody can get in our way now.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:06.09,0:06:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,How much farther?
Dialogue: 9,0:06:08.22,0:06:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We're almost there!
Dialogue: 9,0:06:12.30,0:06:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. The keys are in the ignition.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:14.31,0:06:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha—
Dialogue: 9,0:06:14.97,0:06:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a license, Senpai?
Dialogue: 9,0:06:17.12,0:06:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like this is a public road!
Dialogue: 9,0:06:18.76,0:06:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and hop on, Kuriyama-san!
Dialogue: 9,0:06:21.13,0:06:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey—
Dialogue: 9,0:06:21.76,0:06:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosh!
Dialogue: 9,0:06:24.12,0:06:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,On the handlebar?!
Dialogue: 9,0:06:25.69,0:06:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There are dreamshades up ahead.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:28.00,0:06:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,From below, too!
Dialogue: 9,0:06:38.37,0:06:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Way to go, Kuriyama-san!
Dialogue: 9,0:06:40.43,0:06:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So do I just keep going straight?
Dialogue: 9,0:06:42.65,0:06:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:44.61,0:06:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But you better go as fast as you can!
Dialogue: 9,0:06:47.44,0:06:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,After all,
Dialogue: 9,0:06:49.14,0:06:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,it's too late to hit the brakes!
Dialogue: 9,0:06:53.65,0:06:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 9,0:07:11.74,0:07:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!{You have to be kidding me!}
Dialogue: 9,0:07:25.64,0:07:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 9,0:07:33.18,0:07:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That was absurd.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:35.01,0:07:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This whole place is absurd.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:37.67,0:07:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words,
Dialogue: 9,0:07:38.71,0:07:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,you're absurd.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:40.23,0:07:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?!
Dialogue: 9,0:07:44.48,0:07:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow we made it, though.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:47.62,0:07:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 9,0:07:49.57,0:07:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 9,0:07:54.28,0:07:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Our opponent's in a panic too.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:55.74,0:07:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You can tell?
Dialogue: 9,0:07:56.52,0:07:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:58.28,0:08:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's how I feel.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:01.54,0:08:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure things will work out!
Dialogue: 9,0:08:03.38,0:08:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's kind of unlike you.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:06.48,0:08:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:09.30,0:08:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That said,
Dialogue: 9,0:08:13.51,0:08:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Kuriyama Mirai,
Dialogue: 9,0:08:15.16,0:08:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,am feeling optimistic to an unpleasant degree!
Dialogue: 9,0:08:22.23,0:08:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you running your mouth off for?!
Dialogue: 9,0:08:24.31,0:08:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, can it really hear us?
Dialogue: 9,0:08:27.73,0:08:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How should I know?
Dialogue: 9,0:08:54.72,0:08:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Go for it, Kuriyama-san!
Dialogue: 9,0:09:27.00,0:09:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuriyama-san...
Dialogue: 9,0:09:28.32,0:09:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Akkey...
Dialogue: 9,0:09:31.06,0:09:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost time.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:33.16,0:09:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that the shade beyond the horizon is free of Kuriyama Mirai,
Dialogue: 9,0:09:36.66,0:09:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,it will draw every other dreamshade\Nout there into an ever-widening spiral
Dialogue: 9,0:09:39.99,0:09:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and destroy the world.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:42.38,0:09:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What now,
Dialogue: 9,0:09:44.48,0:09:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi-san?
Dialogue: 9,0:09:52.70,0:09:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuriyama-san?
Dialogue: 9,0:09:54.17,0:09:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuriyama-san.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:55.60,0:09:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuriyama-san!
Dialogue: 9,0:10:01.21,0:10:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't kill us.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:02.58,0:10:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Disgusting.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:03.83,0:10:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You monster.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:04.53,0:10:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so scared.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:06.26,0:10:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Are these my memories?
Dialogue: 9,0:10:10.14,0:10:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 9,0:10:15.46,0:10:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Your younger siblings don't know when to give up,
Dialogue: 9,0:10:18.47,0:10:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,just like you.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:22.76,0:10:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Go for it, big bro.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:24.31,0:10:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuki?
Dialogue: 9,0:10:25.22,0:10:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Leaving this to Izumi-neesama means\Nadmitting that we're as powerless as ever.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:28.74,0:10:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing will change.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:30.88,0:10:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:32.82,0:10:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to your dear Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 9,0:10:36.46,0:10:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiro'omi-senpai's so creepy.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:38.33,0:10:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 9,0:10:42.36,0:10:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you in such a rush?
Dialogue: 9,0:10:45.50,0:10:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the look.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:46.87,0:10:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the look I wanted to see on you.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:49.31,0:10:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That scared and panicked look you try to hide
Dialogue: 9,0:10:53.96,0:10:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,as you struggle to take me down!
Dialogue: 9,0:10:56.00,0:10:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 9,0:10:57.05,0:10:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you that afraid?
Dialogue: 9,0:10:58.69,0:11:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, I don't suppose you {\i1}fancy{\i0} me?
Dialogue: 9,0:11:02.59,0:11:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Or do you just not want your siblings to find out about your past?
Dialogue: 9,0:11:09.46,0:11:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! A spirit hunter who gave in to shades has no right to speak!
Dialogue: 9,0:11:13.02,0:11:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to yourself.
Dialogue: 9,0:11:14.99,0:11:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't we birds of a feather?
Dialogue: 9,0:11:17.07,0:11:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We both harbor shades in our bodies.
Dialogue: 9,0:11:20.51,0:11:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know that,
Dialogue: 9,0:11:21.54,0:11:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,little brother?
Dialogue: 9,0:11:24.76,0:11:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi-neesan...
Dialogue: 9,0:11:28.66,0:11:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 9,0:11:29.63,0:11:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Shut up! Shut up!
Dialogue: 9,0:11:37.48,0:11:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, we may be the same in that regard,
Dialogue: 9,0:11:39.80,0:11:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,but I have yet to abandon\Nmy pride as a human being.
Dialogue: 9,0:11:45.06,0:11:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lump me together\Nwith the likes of you.
Dialogue: 9,0:11:48.40,0:11:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh please, spare me the dramatics.
Dialogue: 9,0:11:58.60,0:11:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Nee-san...
Dialogue: 9,0:12:02.94,0:12:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 9,0:12:05.22,0:12:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably something similar to what showed up back in the Hollow Shadow.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:10.80,0:12:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiro'omi-senpai!
Dialogue: 9,0:12:13.18,0:12:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui?!
Dialogue: 9,0:12:13.92,0:12:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Close your eyes, Kuriyama-san.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:16.40,0:12:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Just do it.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:18.80,0:12:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 9,0:12:22.84,0:12:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be swayed.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:25.10,0:12:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,They say that dreamshades are formed from the twisted human heart and the hatred within, right?{ep3}
Dialogue: 9,0:12:31.68,0:12:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this is a manifestation of the weakness in our hearts.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:35.89,0:12:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you back when we first met?
Dialogue: 9,0:12:38.86,0:12:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you that the same goes for me.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:41.14,0:12:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here by your side.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:44.36,0:12:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We met each other.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:45.99,0:12:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The world changed.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:48.46,0:12:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be a slave to your regrets.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:52.12,0:12:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not alone anymore.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:58.52,0:13:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here for you.
Dialogue: 9,0:13:01.14,0:13:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 9,0:13:02.74,0:13:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Open your eyes.
Dialogue: 9,0:13:12.06,0:13:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 9,0:13:17.80,0:13:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take them out.
Dialogue: 9,0:13:19.60,0:13:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All{\i0} of them?
Dialogue: 9,0:13:21.41,0:13:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a better idea?
Dialogue: 9,0:13:28.26,0:13:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How unpleasant.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:12.60,0:14:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayaka-san!
Dialogue: 9,0:14:14.48,0:14:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ai-chan!
Dialogue: 9,0:14:15.74,0:14:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are okay!
Dialogue: 9,0:14:48.25,0:14:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Did we get them all?
Dialogue: 9,0:14:51.24,0:14:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 9,0:14:59.40,0:15:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty, isn't it?
Dialogue: 9,0:15:02.72,0:15:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 9,0:15:11.26,0:15:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you so terrified of?
Dialogue: 9,0:15:14.32,0:15:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 9,0:15:15.77,0:15:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Every last bit of you is me.
Dialogue: 9,0:15:19.08,0:15:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,All of it used to be inside me.
Dialogue: 9,0:15:22.80,0:15:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Including that sickening envy,
Dialogue: 9,0:15:27.76,0:15:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the despair over the fact that I'll never be human,
Dialogue: 9,0:15:31.28,0:15:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,the sorrow of being abandoned,
Dialogue: 9,0:15:33.20,0:15:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and the regret over hurting someone!
Dialogue: 9,0:15:35.84,0:15:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 9,0:15:36.74,0:15:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And the selfishness, doubt, hatred, resignation, pettiness, and self-preserving attitude!
Dialogue: 9,0:15:43.63,0:15:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let any of it outside!
Dialogue: 9,0:15:46.37,0:15:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It all belongs to me!
Dialogue: 9,0:15:49.29,0:15:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be the one to carry it all!
Dialogue: 9,0:15:54.16,0:15:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the immortal half-shade, you know?
Dialogue: 9,0:16:09.82,0:16:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 9,0:16:21.86,0:16:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai,
Dialogue: 9,0:16:23.68,0:16:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,could you come over here?
Dialogue: 9,0:16:28.76,0:16:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 9,0:16:30.90,0:16:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Er, um, uh...
Dialogue: 9,0:16:35.24,0:16:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I have...
Dialogue: 9,0:16:37.36,0:16:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,a request...
Dialogue: 9,0:16:39.86,0:16:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,A request?
Dialogue: 9,0:16:43.16,0:16:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, please hold out your hand.
Dialogue: 9,0:16:47.65,0:16:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,My hand?
Dialogue: 9,0:16:49.18,0:16:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 9,0:16:58.36,0:17:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Please pat my head.
Dialogue: 9,0:17:01.14,0:17:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to pat my head.
Dialogue: 9,0:17:15.35,0:17:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuriyama-san...
Dialogue: 9,0:17:17.04,0:17:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Say "thank you."
Dialogue: 9,0:17:22.34,0:17:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 9,0:17:23.57,0:17:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Say it like you mean it.
Dialogue: 9,0:17:28.52,0:17:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 9,0:17:35.64,0:17:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So happy...
Dialogue: 9,0:17:38.76,0:17:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 9,0:17:40.68,0:17:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuriyama-san!
Dialogue: 9,0:17:42.54,0:17:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 9,0:17:44.56,0:17:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 9,0:17:47.17,0:17:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuriyama-san, your legs...
Dialogue: 9,0:17:49.32,0:17:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The shade beyond the horizon\Nhas gone back to you,
Dialogue: 9,0:17:53.88,0:17:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,so this place will crumble away soon,
Dialogue: 9,0:17:56.45,0:17:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'll probably disappear along with it.
Dialogue: 9,0:17:59.74,0:18:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that it's gone back to you,
Dialogue: 9,0:18:03.19,0:18:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be able to exist.
Dialogue: 9,0:18:06.08,0:18:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The real me is long gone, after all.
Dialogue: 9,0:18:10.10,0:18:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm truly glad to have met you!
Dialogue: 9,0:18:13.40,0:18:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 9,0:18:14.74,0:18:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm truly glad to have fallen in love with you—
Dialogue: 9,0:18:17.91,0:18:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Don't say it!
Dialogue: 9,0:18:21.42,0:18:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so very much!
Dialogue: 9,0:18:26.41,0:18:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuriyama-san!
Dialogue: 9,0:18:28.04,0:18:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on! This can't be happening!
Dialogue: 9,0:18:30.42,0:18:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuriyama-san!
Dialogue: 9,0:18:33.59,0:18:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuriyama-san!
Dialogue: 9,0:18:49.80,0:18:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody knows if this was all predestined from the start,
Dialogue: 9,0:18:52.27,0:18:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,or if it only happened thanks to Kuriyama-san's efforts.
Dialogue: 9,0:18:56.84,0:18:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But I definitely want to believe it was the latter.
Dialogue: 9,0:19:00.68,0:19:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, the shade from beyond the horizon came back to me,
Dialogue: 9,0:19:04.62,0:19:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and peace was restored to the world.
Dialogue: 9,0:19:07.36,0:19:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,100 yen? Are you for real?!
Dialogue: 9,0:19:10.33,0:19:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm off!
Dialogue: 9,0:19:11.97,0:19:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, morning!
Dialogue: 9,0:19:13.96,0:19:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 9,0:19:16.16,0:19:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful out there.
Dialogue: 9,0:19:17.30,0:19:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 9,0:19:19.26,0:19:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She dozed off!
Dialogue: 9,0:19:20.25,0:19:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Sakura-chan! Wake up!
Dialogue: 9,0:19:22.00,0:19:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Dreamshades exist as they always have,
Dialogue: 9,0:19:24.37,0:19:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and spirit hunters make a living off them as {\i1}they{\i0} always have.
Dialogue: 9,0:19:28.49,0:19:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayaka-san and Ai-chan went back to their place, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.48,0:19:41.86,Sign,,0,0,0,1,{\blur5\t(3500,4400,\blur0.6)\fs25\c&HBB7F68&\frz352.3\pos(1096.33,196.333)}{TS 19:30} 80% Milk
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.48,0:19:41.86,Sign,,0,0,0,2,{\blur5\t(3500,4400,\blur0.6)\fs15\c&H5D6380&\pos(1104,301)}Banana \NAu Lait
Dialogue: 9,0:19:33.84,0:19:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujima Miroku went missing,
Dialogue: 9,0:19:36.21,0:19:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and the Spirit Hunters' Association wrapped everything up nicely
Dialogue: 9,0:19:39.17,0:19:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,by disavowing all knowledge of his actions.
Dialogue: 9,0:19:41.86,0:19:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,One thing did change: Hiro'omi replaced \NIzumi-san as the head of the Nase family.
Dialogue: 9,0:19:48.17,0:19:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But that didn't affect our lives much.
Dialogue: 9,0:19:51.82,0:19:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Nee-san...
Dialogue: 9,0:19:53.36,0:19:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, you will also come to understand.
Dialogue: 9,0:19:57.56,0:19:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 9,0:19:59.52,0:20:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi-neesan.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:01.44,0:20:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You've always been my role model.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:04.03,0:20:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I've lived my entire life wanting to be like you.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:06.73,0:20:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm done with that.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:08.49,0:20:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't turn out like you did.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:10.92,0:20:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand now.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:12.31,0:20:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,When you try to live up to your ideals, sometimes it might not work out.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:16.29,0:20:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But nothing good can come out of giving up on them.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:20.29,0:20:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't be able to protect yourself or those important to you.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:24.98,0:20:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You've grown stronger, Hiro'omi.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:30.44,0:20:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Now listen here, Hiro'omi.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:32.27,0:20:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the Nase family's—
Dialogue: 9,0:20:33.72,0:20:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 9,0:20:35.80,0:20:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Say no more. Not now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.35,0:20:42.72,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\t(30,4368,\fscx107.5)\fscy100\t(30,4368,\fscy107.5)\blur0.6\c&H241F1B&\alpha&H30&\move(652.667,241,633.6,231.16,12,4368)}{TS 20:38} Literature Club
Dialogue: 9,0:20:38.76,0:20:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,As usual, Mitsuki remains cooped up in the \Nclubroom and showers me with verbal abuse.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:42.73,0:20:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}If you know that good will prevail over evil in the end,\Nisn't it a waste of time to continue reading?
Dialogue: 9,0:20:48.99,0:20:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what entertainment's all about, don't you think?
Dialogue: 9,0:20:52.08,0:20:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 9,0:20:53.55,0:20:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's only natural to keep one's hands warm in winter.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:56.21,0:20:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing strange about what I'm doing.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:57.97,0:20:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's totally creepy-crawly!
Dialogue: 9,0:20:59.40,0:20:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Three out of ten.
Dialogue: 9,0:21:04.32,0:21:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,However, Kuriyama Mirai's no longer here.
Dialogue: 9,0:21:07.48,0:21:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.92,0:21:13.56,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\fs15\c&H3F2613&\fnTF2 Professor\b1\move(291,449,330.53,448.98,23,3610)\frz38.6}{TS 21:10} TARGET: 50,{\frz30}000 YEN
Dialogue: 9,0:21:10.66,0:21:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A future built on Kuriyama Mirai's sacrifice holds no meaning at all.
Dialogue: 9,0:21:16.06,0:21:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I yelled out back then, but here I am, having accepted—and living in—that very future.
Dialogue: 9,0:21:21.66,0:21:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure this is what Kuriyama-san's saying right about now:
Dialogue: 9,0:21:25.00,0:21:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,"Serves you right."
Dialogue: 9,0:21:28.08,0:21:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How unpleasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.42,0:21:40.83,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\fs15\c&H4D649C&\an6\pos(639,117)}{TS 21:39} Literature Club Plans for December
Dialogue: 9,0:21:40.12,0:21:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as there is light even at night,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.83,0:21:40.96,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\fs15\c&H4D649C&\an6\pos(639,117)}{TS 21:39}rature Club Plans for December
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.96,0:21:41.08,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\fs15\c&H4D649C&\an6\pos(639,117)}{TS 21:39}ub Plans for December
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.08,0:21:41.21,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\fs15\c&H4D649C&\an6\pos(639,117)}{TS 21:39}b Plans for December
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.21,0:21:41.33,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\fs15\c&H4D649C&\an6\pos(639,117)}{TS 21:39}Plans for December
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.33,0:21:41.46,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\fs15\c&H4D649C&\an6\pos(639,117)}{TS 21:39}b Plans for December
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.46,0:21:41.58,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\fs15\c&H4D649C&\an6\pos(639,117)}{TS 21:39}Club Plans for December
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.58,0:21:41.71,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\fs15\c&H4D649C&\an6\pos(639,117)}{TS 21:39}ure Club Plans for December
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.71,0:21:41.84,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\fs15\c&H4D649C&\an6\pos(639,117)}{TS 21:39}ature Club Plans for December
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.84,0:21:42.29,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\fs15\c&H4D649C&\an6\pos(639,117)}{TS 21:39}rature Club Plans for December
Dialogue: 9,0:21:42.66,0:21:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,just as there are shadows during the day,
Dialogue: 9,0:21:45.37,0:21:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,the world will never be free of darkness.
Dialogue: 9,0:21:48.64,0:21:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,At the same time, it will also never be overcome by it.
